<doc id="413713" wikidata="Q7352246" url="?curid=413713" title="Robin Beanland">
<text>Robin Beanland is a British composer of video game music, composing music for numerous Rare titles, such as the &quot;Killer Instinct&quot; franchise, &quot;Conker&#x27;s Bad Fur Day&quot; (which he also co-wrote the screenplay with Chris Seavor), and many others. Prior to joining Rare, Beanland composed music for TV and films. The only current game that he continues to produce music for is &quot;Sea of Thieves&quot;.

